“Boxes of Toys” is out on Orbeatize Records! Packed in one release a list of rare, expensive gems, quirky takes, library excerpts from the label vaults, otherwise hard to get. 
My lovely @angelina_snf is responsible for the artwork, I also dealt with a couple of transfers from original vinyls. After more than a year spent on chats and emails it’s beautiful finally to have this around. It’s selling fast, so take yours before it’s too late!
